WEBVTT

00:02.300 --> 00:05.100
<i>Cheers</i> is filmed
before a live studio audience.

00:05.200 --> 00:06.299
I don't know, Eddie.

00:06.300 --> 00:08.899
Try-try under the bed.

00:08.900 --> 00:10.199
Well, if they're
not there,

00:10.200 --> 00:11.699
look in the back
of the closet,

00:11.700 --> 00:13.399
or behind the
dresser,

00:13.400 --> 00:14.699
or in the washing
machine.

00:14.700 --> 00:16.600
Yeah, if-if you still
can't find them,

00:16.700 --> 00:17.900
call me back.

00:18.000 --> 00:19.299
I swear to God,

00:19.300 --> 00:20.600
that man would
lose his head

00:20.700 --> 00:21.999
if it weren't
bolted on.

00:22.000 --> 00:23.500
What's, uh...
what's up there, Carla?

00:23.600 --> 00:25.899
Eddie wants to
take the twins
for a walk.

00:25.900 --> 00:27.099
Uh, can't find his shoes, huh?

00:27.100 --> 00:29.200
No, he can't
find the twins.

00:32.700 --> 00:36.100
( <i>piano plays</i> )

00:36.200 --> 00:38.900
