in the world today ¶

00:39.000 --> 00:41.100
¶ Takes everything you've got

00:41.200 --> 00:44.599
¶ Taking a break
from all your worries ¶

00:44.600 --> 00:48.199
¶ Sure would help a lot

00:48.200 --> 00:53.599
¶ Wouldn't you like
to get away? ¶

00:53.600 --> 00:56.299
¶ Sometimes you want to go

00:56.300 --> 01:01.299
¶ Where everybody
